{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Canvas 教學文件","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\"><strong>Canvas API</strong></a></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Canvas tutorial</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_usage\">Basic usage</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_shapes\">Drawing shapes</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">Applying styles and colors</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text\">Drawing text</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">Using images</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Transformations\">Transformations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Compositing\">Compositing and clipping</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_animations\">Basic animations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Advanced_animations\">Advanced animations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Pixel_manipulation_with_canvas\">Pixel manipulation</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Optimizing_canvas\">Optimizing the canvas</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Finale\">Finale</a></li>\n        </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Examples</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/A_basic_ray-caster\">A basic raycaster</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Manipulating_video_using_canvas\">Manipulating video using canvas</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Interfaces</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN\">Documentation:</a></strong></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details>\n      <summary>Contribute</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/MDN\">The MDN project</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\"><strong><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></strong></a> 是一個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a> 元素，我們可以利用程式腳本在這個元素上繪圖（通常是用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>）。除了繪圖，我們還可以合成圖片或做一些簡單（或是<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/HTML/Canvas/A_Basic_RayCaster\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">不那麼簡單</a>）的動畫。右方的影像便是一些運用 &lt;canvas&gt; 的例子，接下來我們將會在教學文件中一一說明。</p>\n<p>本教學從基礎知識開始，描述如何利用 &lt;canvas&gt; 進行 2D 繪圖。教學中的範例會讓各位清楚瞭解 &lt;canvas&gt; 該如何運用，另外也會提供程式碼範例，讓大家嘗試製作自己的內容。</p>\n<p><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> 最早是由 Apple 為 Mac OS X Dashboard 所提出，之後 Safari 和 Google Chrome 也都採用。<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Gecko\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Gecko</a> 1.8 作基礎的瀏覽器，如 Firefox 1.5 也都提供了支援。<code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> 元素是 <a href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WhatWG Web applications 1.0</a>（也就是 HTML5）規範的一部分，目前所有主流的瀏覽器都已支援。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"在開始之前","title":"在開始之前","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> 並不困難，但你需要了解基本的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML\">HTML</a> 與 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>。部分舊版瀏覽器不支援 <code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code>，不過基本上現今所有主流的瀏覽器都有支援。預設的畫布大小是 300px * 150px（寬 * 高）。但你也可以透過 HTML 寬、高屬性（<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Attribute\">attribute</a>）自訂。為了在畫布上作畫，我們使用了一個 JavaScript context 物件來即時繪製圖形。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"教學文件","title":"教學文件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_usage\">基本用途</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_shapes\">繪製圖形</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">套用樣式與顏色</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text\">繪製文字</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">使用影像</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Transformations\">變形效果</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Compositing\">合成效果</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_animations\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">基礎動畫 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Advanced_animations\">進階動畫</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Pixel_manipulation_with_canvas\">像素控制</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Hit_regions_and_accessibility\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Hit regions and accessibility</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Optimizing_canvas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">最佳化 canvas (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Finale\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finale (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas topic page</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://visitmix.com/labs/ai2canvas/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Adobe Illustrator to Canvas plug-in</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.html5canvastutorials.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5CanvasTutorials</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://creativejs.com/2011/08/31-days-of-canvas-tutorials/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">31 days of canvas tutorials</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Drawing Graphics with Canvas (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/tag/Canvas_examples\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Canvas examples</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://html5tutorial.com\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 Tutorial</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text\">Drawing Text Using a Canvas</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/library/safari/#documentation/AudioVideo/Conceptual/HTML-canvas-guide/AddingText/AddingText.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/TP40010542-CH6-SW4\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Adding Text to Canvas</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.canvasdemos.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas Demos - Games, applications, tools and tutorials</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://canvimation.github.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas Drawing and Animation Application</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://billmill.org/static/canvastutorial/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">interactive canvas tutorial</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://blog.nihilogic.dk/2009/02/html5-canvas-cheat-sheet.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Canvas Cheat Sheet with all attributes and methods</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://visitmix.com/labs/ai2canvas/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Adobe Illustrator to Canvas plug-in</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.html5canvastutorials.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5CanvasTutorials</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://html5tutorial.com/how-to-draw-n-grade-bezier-curve-with-canvas-api\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">How to draw N grade Bézier curves with the Canvas API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://creativejs.com/2011/08/31-days-of-canvas-tutorials/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">31 days of canvas tutorials</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2dcontext/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C Standard</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"致歉各位貢獻者","title":"致歉各位貢獻者","isH3":false,"content":"<p>由於 2013/6/17 那一週的不幸技術錯誤，所有有關本教學的歷史紀錄，包括過去所有貢獻者的紀錄都遺失了，我們深感抱歉，希望各位可以原諒這一次不幸的意外。</p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    \n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_usage\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"在開始之前","id":"在開始之前"},{"text":"教學文件","id":"教學文件"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"},{"text":"致歉各位貢獻者","id":"致歉各位貢獻者"}],"summary":"<canvas> 是一個 HTML 元素，我們可以利用程式腳本在這個元素上繪圖（通常是用 JavaScript）。除了繪圖，我們還可以合成圖片或做一些簡單（或是不那麼簡單）的動畫。右方的影像便是一些運用 <canvas> 的例子，接下來我們將會在教學文件中一一說明。","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Canvas tutorial","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Tutorial Canvas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Tutoriel canvas","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Canvas チュートリアル","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"캔버스 튜토리얼","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Canvas tutorial","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Руководство по Canvas","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Canvas 教程","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/canvas_api/tutorial","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/canvas_api/tutorial/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API","title":"Canvas API"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial","title":"Canvas 教學文件"}],"pageTitle":"Canvas 教學文件 - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}